text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria bryonicola is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Jamaica.
text.Sources: World Conservation Monitoring Centre (1998). "Psychotria bryonicola". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T33864A9815688. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33864A9815688.en. Retrieved 16 December 2017.
